Below is a list of the various Slippyfop Games along with how they interact with your data:
Drink To That – Drinking Game
Majority Rules
Conversation Breaker
HexDash
D’tox
Block Swipe
Drink to that – Drinking game
Version 9 and below use AdMob from Google to show ads in this app. AdMob wants to show ads relevant to you and uses the device’s advertising ID to serve personalized ads based on the user’s interests.
Version 10 and above uses IronSource to Show Ads. Ironsource will show ads relevant to you and use the device’s advertising ID to serve personalized ads based on the user’s interest.
Please check the in-game options to see what version you are playing on.
In compliance with the GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation), users in the EEA (European Economic Area) will see a message asking for their consent.
For more information on how IronSource handles your data, please read:
https://developers.is.com/ironsource-mobile/air/ironsource-mobile-privacy-policy/
Read all about the Google page to opt out of customized advertising:
https://adssettings.google.com/u/0/authenticated.
And here is the link to Google’s Privacy Policies:
https://policies.google.com/privacy
and
https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites
.
Drink To That uses Firebase Crashlytics and Firebase Analytics by Google for capturing automatic crash reports, usage statistics data, and demographics data. We do not use or store any PII data via this service. The data that we can get is anonymous and purely statistical. Get to know all about Firebase Privacy Policy:
https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy
.
Drink To That features optional User Accounts. These accounts are handled using Firebase Authentication.
Majority Rules
We use AdMob from Google to show ads in this app. AdMob wants to show ads relevant to you and uses the device’s advertising ID to serve personalized ads based on the user’s interests.
In compliance with the GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation), users in the EEA (European Economic Area) will see a message asking for their consent.
Read all about the Google page to opt out of customized advertising:
https://adssettings.google.com/u/0/authenticated.
