D’tox
This game collects advertiser data that is shared with third parties. All other data is primarily used for advertising data and is controlled by Unity Ads.
For more information on how Unity Ads shares and manages your data, see
https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy#:~:text=Unity%20Ads%3A%20We%20may%20utilize,viewed%20or%20interacted%20with%20ads.
